and said I did everything right.

55
00:04:29,108 --> 00:04:30,708
"Played by the rules."

56
00:04:32,090 --> 00:04:34,847
The only thing is
the world's changed a lot since 1982.

57
00:04:35,428 --> 00:04:36,807
It's more predatory.

58
00:04:36,991 --> 00:04:39,403
The minute we assumed responsibility

59
00:04:39,528 --> 00:04:41,275
the bloggers, the press,

60
